menu "Example Configuration"

    config ENABLE_ALIRO_BLE_UWB
        bool "Enable Aliro (Apple Home Key) over BLE + UWB"
        default y
        help
            Advertise the Door Lock cluster's Aliro Provisioning + BLE-UWB
            features and register the Aliro reader delegate, so Apple Home can
            provision an Express (BLE + UWB) Home Key into Wallet for this reader.

endmenu
